♪I saw you approaching me♪

107
00:14:42,330 --> 00:14:45,590
♪My smile became clearer♪

108
00:14:46,050 --> 00:14:49,990
♪We met, and you left♪

109
00:14:53,420 --> 00:14:56,690
♪Watching you going away♪

110
00:14:57,170 --> 00:15:00,520
♪Further and further
until you disappeared♪

111
00:15:00,910 --> 00:15:04,610
♪Nothing left but a gentle sigh♪

112
00:15:06,400 --> 00:15:10,480
♪In my hard days, I dreamed about you♪

113
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:14,050
♪In my dreams, you saw my heart♪

114
00:15:14,050 --> 00:15:19,530
♪When the daylight came,
I couldn't bear to wake up♪

115
00:15:21,180 --> 00:15:25,120
♪You are the prettiest reflection
in the water♪

116
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:28,700
♪The image of your face
is closer than the mirage♪

117
00:15:28,700 --> 00:15:34,920
♪As if I can touch it
when I reach out my hand♪

118
00:15:35,740 --> 00:15:37,830
♪You've seen seasons change♪

119
00:15:37,830 --> 00:15:41,400
♪You've seen winds, clouds,
mountains, and seas♪

120
00:15:41,420 --> 00:15:43,220
You're seriously injured.

121
00:15:43,820 --> 00:15:45,380
Why did you move?

122
00:15:47,260 --> 00:15:49,860
Just trying to reach your scarf.

123
00:15:50,450 --> 00:15:52,620
♪Even if it's covered with dust♪

124
00:15:52,620 --> 00:15:55,850
♪Ignored, forgotten,
sealed, and buried♪

125
00:15:55,860 --> 00:15:57,500
Let's go to the hospital.

126
00:15:58,060 --> 00:16:05,120
♪As time flies by,
it'll remain unchanged♪

127
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:24,360
♪In my hard days, I dreamed about you♪

128
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:27,920
♪In my dreams, you saw my heart♪

129
00:16:27,920 --> 00:16:29,560
♪When the daylight came♪

130
00:16:29,780 --> 00:16:30,940
Don't worry.

131
00:16:32,020 --> 00:16:33,100
I'm not gonna die.

132
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:38,920
♪You are the prettiest reflection
in the water♪

133
00:16:38,920 --> 00:16:42,650
♪The image of your face
is closer than the mirage♪

134
00:16:42,650 --> 00:16:49,260
♪As if I can touch it
when I reach out my hand♪

135
00:17:34,860 --> 00:17:35,700
Miss.

136
00:17:37,380 --> 00:17:38,780
Has Xiao Xiao

137
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:40,060
taken any action?

138
00:17:41,220 --> 00:17:42,540
Not yet.

139
00:17:43,260 --> 00:17:44,860
Xiang Tingdong is complicated,

140
00:17:47,460 --> 00:17:48,980
so is Xiao Xiao.

141
00:17:49,540 --> 00:17:51,060
She won't go easy on him.

142
00:17:59,300 --> 00:18:00,300
Xin Yi.

143
00:18:02,980 --> 00:18:04,300
All this time,

144
00:18:11,580 --> 00:18:13,500
have I been too selfish?

145
00:18:14,620 --> 00:18:16,020
No, Miss.

146
00:18:16,420 --> 00:18:18,060
You had no choice.

147
00:18:21,660 --> 00:18:22,500
By the way,

148
00:18:23,140 --> 00:18:24,340
how's everything going at home?

149
00:18:24,780 --> 00:18:26,100
Ms. Ruolan wants to see you.

150
00:18:38,820 --> 00:18:40,980
Aunt, what's the matter?

151
00:18:41,300 --> 00:18:42,140
Cheng,

152
00:18:42,700 --> 00:18:43,860
is Tingdong alright?

153
00:18:46,220 --> 00:18:47,620
He's fine.

154
00:18:48,060 --> 00:18:50,380
I'm not talking about
the one lying in bed.

155
00:18:55,620 --> 00:18:57,220
I'm referring to my nephew

156
00:18:57,420 --> 00:18:58,700
Xiang Tingdong.

157
00:19:07,260 --> 00:19:08,300
Aunt...

158
00:19:09,140 --> 00:19:09,980
Tingdong...

159
00:19:09,980 --> 00:19:11,340
Since you were a kid,

160
00:19:11,540 --> 00:19:13,540
you've had the habit of making a fist

161
00:19:13,860 --> 00:19:15,140
when you're nervous or lying.

162
00:19:19,780 --> 00:19:20,620
Tell me.

163
00:19:21,020 --> 00:19:22,220
Where is Tingdong?

164
00:19:22,420 --> 00:19:23,780
What really happened?

165
00:19:25,060 --> 00:19:25,900
I...

166
