Everyone in Tangcheng knows

167
00:19:28,380 --> 00:19:30,340
what happened at New Fairy tonight.

168
00:19:30,540 --> 00:19:31,620
I know my nephew

169
00:19:31,780 --> 00:19:32,940
very well.

170
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:38,180
Aunt...

171
00:19:39,540 --> 00:19:40,380
Tell me.

172
